{"tid":1821653,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"支那男便秘誤信偏方吞鱔魚 腸道被咬出大洞命","createTime":"2020-01-12T12:35:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T03:35:37.000Z","uid":32511,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ab9e5d06c3266e1f09e3d7b40a29d590302f9353","tid":1821653,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T12:35:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.news.ebc.net.tw/EbcNews/news/2020/01/12/1578842399_58980.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.news.ebc.net.tw%2FEbcNews%2Fnews%2F2020%2F01%2F12%2F1578842399_58980.jpg&h=9b2daa17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n便祕是現代人常有的腸胃問題，大陸南京有位男子因聽信「生吞黃鱔（鱔魚）能治便秘」，為了改善身體狀況，他生吞了2條50公分長、3公分粗的活鱔魚，沒想到不但便秘情況沒有緩解，反而導致他腹痛難耐，只好趕緊就醫。醫生用電腦斷層掃瞄後發現，鱔魚竟在男子腸道亂竄，還咬出約2公分的大洞，情況相當危險。<br />\n<br />\n根據陸媒報導，該名51歲男子9日中午時，因為腹部劇痛被工地同事送到當地醫院的急診室，男子向醫生坦承，自己前一天為治療便秘和前列腺炎，生吞了2條活鱔魚，卻因此腹痛難耐。男子坦言，原本想說忍耐一下，疼痛就會改善，不料第二天就受不了只好就醫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.news.ebc.net.tw/EbcNews/news/2020/01/12/1578840145_62081.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.news.ebc.net.tw%2FEbcNews%2Fnews%2F2020%2F01%2F12%2F1578840145_62081.jpg&h=bbc45db2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.news.ebc.net.tw/EbcNews/news/2020/01/12/1578840161_64903.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.news.ebc.net.tw%2FEbcNews%2Fnews%2F2020%2F01%2F12%2F1578840161_64903.jpg&h=e7b327d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫生檢查了男子身體後，驚訝發現患者已經出現腸道穿孔、瀰漫性腹膜炎、感染性休克的狀況，恐有生命危險。醫生表示男子的下腹部腹腔裡，有2隻很粗的黃鱔亂竄，更在乙狀結腸附近，距離腹腔約10公分處，看見一個將近2公分的穿孔，「因為鱔魚吞進去是活的，人的腸道又比較薄弱，因此被撕咬後就容易鑽出孔來。」<br />\n<br />\n據悉，男子動完手術後移往加護病房，仍未脫離險境。對此有網友感到疑惑，要如何生吞50公分的鱔魚而不噎住致命？胃酸不會將鱔魚分解？懷疑這件事並不單純，「我覺得不太可能從上面的口吞下去」、「無知釀成的苦果」，也有人看過類似案例，「有次看到一個日本人生吞一碗小魚，頓時感覺很厲害」。"},{"pid":"d1567dc33f724269f6eae27fdc42efefdcce20fc","tid":1821653,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T12:37:53.000Z","msg":"劣種淘汰 物競天擇"},{"pid":"533a98e8c0bb517e742443def5289865353411d8","tid":1821653,"uid":4001,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T12:37:59.000Z","msg":"「我覺得不太可能從上面的口吞下去」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eb56b6e553f63f7cfb3c36398620c46678b7364","tid":1821653,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T12:38:14.000Z","msg":"擺明係下面塞入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"730c34ac1fa9a36ac8b3b4302a184ddc543376da","tid":1821653,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T12:39:54.000Z","msg":"吞既話落到胃都俾胃酸拿死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bea12808bcdc6b1967b86952f3d8c4d74cd8599c","tid":1821653,"uid":118082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T12:41:23.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1028a7d3391f859ff64bfe33ef78b6634b4d4c","tid":1821653,"uid":2267,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"533a98e8c0bb517e742443def5289865353411d8","tid":1821653,"uid":4001,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T12:37:59.000Z","msg":"「我覺得不太可能從上面的口吞下去」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:30:08.000Z","msg":"好明顯從屎眼塞入去，點知太爽，入多條<br />\n以為會捐返出嚟，等咗成日頂唔順先入院"},{"pid":"8c96c8f5abedabfb33bc1a06c4f281999bfc7f86","tid":1821653,"uid":24310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc1028a7d3391f859ff64bfe33ef78b6634b4d4c","tid":1821653,"uid":2267,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"533a98e8c0bb517e742443def5289